title: Cold Case: Missing Lindsey Baum
itunes:title: Cold Case: Missing Lindsey Baum
description:
10-year-old Lindsey Baum disappeared without a trace while walking home from a neighborhood pool party in Washington State community in 2009. Nancy Grace talks with her mom, Melissa Baum, about the latest developments in her case and why she still believes her daughter is alive.
